or fainter\nmagnitudes with increasing age as well as a trend for brighter magnitudes with\nincreasing apparent cluster radii.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2010 05:45:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
